{"result": {"folders": ["2019", "lecture13"], "nr": 1312, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "created": "2019-04-23T09:53:59Z", "bucket_order": 3, "no_answer_followup": 0, "change_log": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "jshne0ytr8i4nb", "data": "jutm3vjeq283cp", "type": "create", "when": "2019-04-23T09:53:59Z"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "data": "jutpg9lnjm5225", "to": "jutm3vjcezu3cn", "type": "i_answer", "when": "2019-04-23T11:27:36Z"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "jshne0ytr8i4nb", "subject": "期中虚拟页式存储实现写时复制&#xff0c;虚拟段式为什么不可以", "created": "2019-04-23T09:53:59Z", "content": "期中虚拟页式存储实现写时复制&#xff0c;虚拟段式为什么不可以\n中虚拟段式系统中&#xff0c;进程每次fork都复制一遍&#xff0c;开销大&#xff0c;当需要写的时候再复制可以在一些特殊情况下减少这部分开销\n虽然堆栈段全部复制开销依然很大&#xff0c;但首先这是虚拟段式存储自身的弊端&#xff0c;并不影响写时复制在这上面的利用。其次可以利用段的特点&#xff0c;让动态内存的大小可变&#xff0c;将一个大段分成若干小段&#xff0c;写时复制对应小段。\n不知这样想法有和漏洞&#xff0c;望告知。"}], "type": "question", "tags": ["2019", "lecture13", "student"], "tag_good": [], "unique_views": 84, "children": [{"folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "children": [], "created": "2019-04-23T11:27:36Z", "bucket_order": 3, "tag_endorse": [{"role": "student", "name": "289212182@qq.com", "endorser": {}, "admin": false, "photo": "1551463481_35.png", "id": "j7f1tr6wJNH", "photo_url": "https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/photos/j7f1tr6wJNH/1551463481_35.png", "published": true, "us": false, "facebook_id": null}, {"role": "student", "name": "张泽阳2016010425", "endorser": {}, "admin": false, "photo": null, "id": "jsk1to9nLhla", "photo_url": null, "published": true, "us": false, "facebook_id": null}], "bucket_name": "Today", "id": "jutpg9licrs224", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "subject": "", "created": "2019-04-23T11:27:36Z", "content": "<p>写时复制COW是基于页来讨论的&#xff0c;并没有基于段的COW。COW需要VMA和PT的同时参与&#xff0c;而在段式管理时也是没有的。基于这些原因&#xff0c;在段式时&#xff0c;基于COW的fork是无法实现的。</p>"}], "type": "i_answer", "tag_endorse_arr": ["j7f1tr6wJNH", "jsk1to9nLhla"], "config": {}, "is_tag_endorse": false}], "tag_good_arr"